headline: Did FICO’s Latest Responsible AI Patents Just Shift Its Competitive Investment Narrative?
summary: FICO recently announced it has been awarded 10 new patents in Responsible AI and transaction analytics, marking significant advances in areas such as bias detection, fraud prevention, data privacy, and model accuracy across its technology platforms. This patent milestone comes as FICO prepares to report its fourth quarter earnings and faces growing competition in its mortgage scoring business, following regulatory changes allowing alternative scoring models for government-backed...
